### 4. Search season by season name
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search-by-season/first

### 5. Add a new season
POST http://localhost:3000/api/add-season
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 112,
  "season":"first",
  "years": "2023-2024"
}

### 6. Delete a season by id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/delete-season/1